description:
The gospel is simple: Christ died in order to offer life for those who dont deserve it. Thats what grace is all about. In this program, called Mortal Enemies Gary Kent uses an amazing story to teach us a lesson about grace. Don't miss it this Sunday (6 October) on channel 9GEM at 8:30am across Australia.
